00:11:09,686 --> 00:11:10,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

184
00:11:12,989 --> 00:11:14,157
<font color=#FFFF00>Terdengar parah, kan?</font>

185
00:11:14,524 --> 00:11:15,858
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia terkena <i>emfisema</i> paru.</font>

186
00:11:15,858 --> 00:11:16,893
<font color=#FFFF00>Suhu?</font>

187
00:11:16,893 --> 00:11:18,361
<font color=#FFFF00>Hingga 38,5 ° C.</font>

188
00:11:18,361 --> 00:11:19,395
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Emfisema paru adalah suatu masalah
pada paru-paru.)</i></font>

189
00:11:20,129 --> 00:11:21,764
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan meraba perutnya.
/ Baik.</font>

190
00:11:22,331 --> 00:11:24,901
<font color=#FFFF00>Pak, aku akan menurunkan sabuk celanamu.</font>

191
00:11:25,134 --> 00:11:26,636
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong aku.
/ Baik.</font>

192
00:11:28,037 --> 00:11:30,139
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan berusaha untuk membantu.
Kami akan melakukannya.</font>

193
00:11:30,306 --> 00:11:31,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Biar kulihat.</font>

194
00:11:34,077 --> 00:11:35,144
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini hernia.</font>

195
00:11:36,012 --> 00:11:37,480
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak bisa menyembuhkannya secara manual.</font>

196
00:11:38,047 --> 00:11:39,782
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku perlu memeriksa dengan USG...,</font>

197
00:11:39,782 --> 00:11:42,752
<font color=#FFFF00>...namun berdasarkan demamnya,
bisa dikatakan itu <i>hernia strangulata</i>.</font>

198
00:11:42,752 --> 00:11:45,455
<font color=#FFFF00>Ususnya yang terpuntir memotong sirkulasi
dan mulai membusuk.</font>

199
00:11:45,455 --> 00:11:47,990
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau bisa menyembuhkan dia dengan operasi?</font>

200
00:11:48,391 --> 00:11:49,726
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo kita cek dulu.</font>

201
00:11:49,992 --> 00:11:52,295
<font color=#FFFF00>Ambilkan alat USG.
/ Baik.</font>

202
00:12:04,707 --> 00:12:06,142
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini hernia strangulata.</font>

203
00:12:08,111 --> 00:12:09,779
<font color=#FFFF00>Hasil tes darah.</font>

204
00:12:12,248 --> 00:12:13,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Denyut nadinya semakin cepat.</font>

205
00:12:13,850 --> 00:12:15,284
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus mengoperasinya sekarang.</font>

206
00:12:25,628 --> 00:12:26,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa indeks INR-nya...</font>

207
00:12:26,929 --> 00:12:28,297
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Indeks INR mengukur pembekuan darah.)</i></font>

208
00:12:33,002 --> 00:12:34,771
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak bisa mengoperasi?
/ Tidak.</font>

209
00:12:34,771 --> 00:12:36,606
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bilang kita bisa.
/ Dia bilang iya.</font>

210
00:12:36,606 --> 00:12:37,607
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku yang menghentikannya.</font>

211
00:12:37,607 --> 00:12:39,375
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat dokter bedah mengatakan iya?</font>

212
00:12:39,742 --> 00:12:42,245
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu bukan transplantasi. Itu hanya hernia.</font>

213
00:12:43,546 --> 00:12:45,848
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia sangat ahli menggunakan pisau bedah
dan menyembuhkannya.</font>

214
00:12:45,848 --> 00:12:47,083
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia harus membedahnya.</font>

215
00:12:47,650 --> 00:12:50,453
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak ada operasi yang mudah,
dan pasien ini...</font>

216
00:12:52,155 --> 00:12:53,189
<font color=#FFFF00>...tidak bisa dibius.</font>

217
00:12:53,723 --> 00:12:55,925
<font color=#FFFF00>Emfisema paru nya terlalu parah.</font>

218
00:12:56,125 --> 00:12:57,960
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia tidak akan bertahan
dengan anestesi umum.</font>

219
00:12:58,060 --> 00:12:59,495
<font color=#FFFF00>Bius dia dari pinggang ke bawah.</font>

220
00:12:59,929 --> 00:13:02,031
<font color=#FFFF00>Bius tulang belakangnya
seperti pasien <i>sclera</i> pecah.</font>

221
00:13:03,099 --> 00:13:04,100
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak.</font>

222
00:13:05,268 --> 00:13:06,669
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tahu alasannya, kan?</font>

223
00:13:07,170 --> 00:13:08,504
<font color=#FFFF00>Karena <i>warfarin</i>?</font>

224
00:13:08,838 --> 00:13:10,239
<font color=#FFFF00>Setelah operasi otaknya...</font>

225
00:13:10,239 --> 00:13:11,274
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Warfarin mengencerkan darah)</i></font>

226
00:13:11,274 --> 00:13:12,809
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia harus terus menahannya.</font>

227
00:13:14,177 --> 00:13:15,411
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita tidak bisa menghentikan pendarahan.</font>

228
00:13:16,546 --> 00:13:18,815
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika terbentuk gumpalan darah
di sumsum tulang belakang nya...,</font>

229
00:13:19,148 --> 00:13:21,584
<font color=#FFFF00>...itu bisa menimbulkan risiko
pada sistem saraf.</font>

230
00:13:22,819 --> 00:13:25,221
<font color=#FFFF00>Ada <i>septicemia</i> dan infeksi juga.
<i>(*banyak bakteri di dalam darah)</i></font>

231
00:13:25,221 --> 00:13:26,889
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan sebelum operasi, anestesi...</font>

232
00:13:26,889 --> 00:13:27,957
<font color=#FFFF00>...bisa membunuhnya.</font>

233
00:13:33,663 --> 00:13:35,431
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau bilang
itu mungkin untuk dilakukan?</font>

234
00:13:36,432 --> 00:13:38,267
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa yang bisa kau lakukan?</font>

235
00:13:39,902 --> 00:13:42,104
<font color=#FFFF00>Menggunakan <i>lidokain</i> secara lokal.
/ Apa?</font>

236
00:13:42,171 --> 00:13:43,472
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku bilang itu mustahil.</font>

237
00:13:43,539 --> 00:13:46,108
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika kita tidak melakukan apa-apa,
dia akan mati karena <i>septikemia</i>.</font>

238
00:13:46,576 --> 00:13:49,178
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini tetap berbahaya, bahkan
jika kita menggunakan anestesi lokal.</font>

239
00:13:50,479 --> 00:13:52,582
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pikir pasien bisa menahan rasa sakit?</font>

240
00:13:52,682 --> 00:13:55,785
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia akan mengepalkan otot-otot perutnya.
Bisakah kau melaluinya?</font>

241
00:13:55,785 --> 00:13:57,687
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan memberinya propofol
dan dalam satu jam...</font>

242
00:13:57,687 --> 00:13:59,822
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter.
/ Mencapai hernia...,</font>

243
00:13:59,822 --> 00:14:01,390
<font color=#FFFF00>dan meminimalisir resiko.</font>

244
00:14:01,591 --> 00:14:03,025
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhenti menghayal.</font>

245
00:14:03,025 --> 00:14:05,394
<font color=#FFFF00>Kasus serupa ada dalam catatan Dokter Kwak.</font>

246
00:14:05,561 --> 00:14:07,063
<font color=#FFFF00>Saya cukup mempelajarinya, jadi...</font>

247
00:14:07,063 --> 00:14:08,598
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu di zona perang.</font>

248
00:14:08,931 --> 00:14:10,600
<font color=#FFFF00>Mereka tidak punya pun,
sehingga mereka harus...</font>

249
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:11,634
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa bedanya dengan sekarang?</font>

250
00:14:11,701 --> 00:14:14,170
<font color=#FFFF00>Alat dan obat-obatan kita tidak berguna.</font>

251
00:14:14,170 --> 00:14:16,739
<font color=#FFFF00>Tunggu. Biarkan aku meluruskan ini.</font>

252
00:14:18,174 --> 00:14:20,576
<font color=#FFFF00>Masalah satu-satunya adalah anestesi, kan?</font>

253
00:14:21,444 --> 00:14:23,145
<font color=#FFFF00>Kalau begitu aku bisa membantu.</font>

254
00:14:26,983 --> 00:14:28,184
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana?</font>

255
00:14:28,584 --> 00:14:31,087
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini mungkin mustahil untuk dipercaya...</font>

256
00:14:31,520 --> 00:14:32,855
<font color=#FFFF00>...atau disetujui.</font>

257
00:14:34,757 --> 00:14:36,926
<font color=#FFFF00>Anestesi akupunktur adalah bidangku.</font>

258
00:14:37,260 --> 00:14:39,362
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini konsentrasiku...</font>

259
00:14:39,662 --> 00:14:41,364
<font color=#FFFF00>..saat magang dan <i>residensi</i>.</font>

260
00:14:41,364 --> 00:14:43,666
<font color=#FFFF00>Jae Geol, aku mengerti bagaimana perasaanmu.</font>

261
00:14:43,666 --> 00:14:44,734
<font color=#FFFF00>Lihat ini.</font>

262
00:14:44,734 --> 00:14:47,503
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkin mustahil untuk mengoperasi
hanya dengan anestesi akupunktur.</font>

263
00:14:48,204 --> 00:14:50,273
<font color=#FFFF00>Gunakan anestesi lokal dengan <i>lidokain</i>.</font>

264
00:14:50,273 --> 00:14:52,975
<font color=#FFFF00>Lalu gunakan anestesi akupunktur
dengan obat penenang.</font>

265
00:14:52,975 --> 00:14:54,877
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini bukan anestesi umum...,</font>

266
00:14:56,178 --> 00:14:58,281
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi bisa memiliki efek yang sama.
/ Jae Geol.</font>

267
00:14:58,281 --> 00:15:00,283
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tahu itu sulit untuk percaya. Namun...</font>

268
00:15:01,250 --> 00:15:03,986
<font color=#FFFF00>Bahkan jika tidak memiliki efek sama sekali...,</font>

269
00:15:05,521 --> 00:15:07,556
<font color=#FFFF00>...kita harus mencobanya.</font>

270
00:15:08,024 --> 00:15:11,127
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu bukan obat bius anestesi. Tidak akan
meninggalkan bekas pada tulang belakang.</font>

271
00:15:11,127 --> 00:15:13,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu tidak akan membahayakan pasien sama sekali.</font>

272
00:15:20,336 --> 00:15:22,104
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau harus melakukannya tidak peduli apapun.</font>

273
00:15:23,072 --> 00:15:24,273
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak boleh...</font>

274
00:15:25,241 --> 00:15:28,077
<font color=#FFFF00>...kehilangan pasien itu.</font>

275
00:15:28,911 --> 00:15:31,047
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak boleh kehilangan pasien juga.</font>

276
00:15:31,314 --> 00:15:32,782
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagiku...</font>

277
00:15:35,117 --> 00:15:37,286
<font color=#FFFF00>...dia lebih berharga dari ayahku.</font>

278
00:15:42,258 --> 00:15:43,826
<font color=#FFFF00>Ahli bedah...</font>

279
00:15:44,493 --> 00:15:47,229
<font color=#FFFF00>Dengarlah, Hyun. Aku...</font>

280
00:15:50,366 --> 00:15:51,500
<font color=#FFFF00>Haruskah kita...</font>

281
00:15:52,568 --> 00:15:53,970
<font color=#FFFF00>...mencobanya?</font>

282
00:15:58,641 --> 00:16:01,677
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau akan mengoperasi meskipun
dengan anestesi lokal.</font>

283
00:16:01,844 --> 00:16:03,879
<font color=#FFFF00>Jika operasi diperlukan...,</font>

284
00:16:04,080 --> 00:16:05,915
<font color=#FFFF00>...Aku butuh satu lagi tindakan pengamanan.</font>

285
00:16:05,915 --> 00:16:09,151
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisakah anestesi akupunktur
menjadi tindakan pengamanan?</font>

286
00:16:09,986 --> 00:16:12,788
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita tidak punya banyak pilihan.</font>

287
00:16:13,356 --> 00:16:16,692
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus mengurangi rasa sakit
untuk meminimalkan risiko.</font>

288
00:16:16,692 --> 00:16:20,629
<font color=#FFFF00>Kita harus melakukan segala yang kita bisa...</font>

289
00:16:21,097 --> 00:16:23,499
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk mengurangi rasa sakit pada pasien.</font>

290
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,501
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu pendapatku.</font>

291
00:16:25,935 --> 00:16:29,672
<font color=#FFFF00>Dia bilang itu tidak berbahaya
meskipun dalam skenario kasus terburuk.</font>

292
00:16:30,439 --> 00:16:31,607
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter.</font>

293
00:16:36,312 --> 00:16:37,613
<font color=#FFFF00>Baiklah.</font>

294
00:16:39,181 --> 00:16:41,984
<font color=#FFFF00>Benarkah?
/ Mari kita coba.</font>

295
00:16:46,422 --> 00:16:48,257
<font color=#FFFF00>Lepaskan aku.</font>

296
00:16:48,257 --> 00:16:51,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan lenganmu.
/ Biarkan aku pergi.</font>

297
00:16:51,861 --> 00:16:55,131
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku akan mati seperti ini...</font>

298
00:16:55,131 --> 00:16:57,933
<font color=#FFFF00>...dengan mata terbuka lebar.</font>

299
00:16:57,933 --> 00:17:00,669
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa kau membedah perutku?</font>

300
00:17:00,669 --> 00:17:02,705
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhentilah keras kepala, Pak.</font>

301
00:17:02,705 --> 00:17:04,473
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau perlu pembedahan.</font>

302
00:17:04,473 --> 00:17:05,941
<font color=#FFFF00>Menjauh dariku!</font>

303
00:17:06,442 --> 00:17:10,479
<font color=#FFFF00>Oh, Ya Tuhan.</font>

304
00:17:12,248 --> 00:17:13,382
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga.</font>

305
00:17:14,450 --> 00:17:16,085
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisakah kau...</font>

306
00:17:16,452 --> 00:17:19,588
<font color=#FFFF00>...membantuku bangun? Tolong?</font>

307
00:17:20,423 --> 00:17:21,590
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pergi.</font>

308
00:17:22,124 --> 00:17:25,394
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin pergi ke suatu tempat...</font>

309
00:17:25,394 --> 00:17:27,963
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan mati seperti ini.</font>

310
00:17:27,963 --> 00:17:29,365
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu saja.</font>

311
00:17:30,599 --> 00:17:33,636
<font color=#FFFF00>Tolong melepaskan aku.</font>

312
00:17:33,636 --> 00:17:36,639
<font color=#FFFF00>Kubilang biarkan aku pergi.</font>

313
00:17:51,854 --> 00:17:54,790
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jae Geol, ayo kita pulang.</i></font>

314
00:17:55,424 --> 00:17:58,527
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tidak, lepaskan aku.</i></font>

315
00:17:59,562 --> 00:18:00,930
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku  pergi.</i></font>

316
00:18:01,664 --> 00:18:03,499
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku akan pergi ke mana pun...</i></font>

317
00:18:05,534 --> 00:18:07,436
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...dan bunuh diri.</i></font>

318
00:18:07,436 --> 00:18:10,706
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Astaga, kau tidak boleh mengatakan...</i></font>

319
00:18:10,706 --> 00:18:13,175
<font color=#FFFF00><i>...hal buruk seperti itu.</i></font>

320
00:18:13,509 --> 00:18:16,912
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku akan memperbaiki sepedamu.</i></font>

321
00:18:17,646 --> 00:18:20,349
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Tidak, jangan.</i></font>

322
00:18:21,350 --> 00:18:23,919
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku benci Ibu dan Ayah.</i></font>

323
00:18:23,953 --> 00:18:25,855
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Aku akan bunuh diri.</i></font>

324
00:18:25,855 --> 00:18:27,156
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jae Geol.</i></font>

325
00:18:27,823 --> 00:18:29,258
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau masih anak kecil.</i></font>

326
00:18:29,558 --> 00:18:32,061
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Jangan mengatakan hal buruk seperti itu.</i></font>

327
00:18:32,528 --> 00:18:33,796
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Kau mengerti?</i></font>

328
00:18:44,507 --> 00:18:46,208
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau menjadi pemarah?</font>

329
00:18:47,443 --> 00:18:49,712
<font color=#FFFF00>Akulah orang yang pandai
menjadi pemarah.</font>

330
00:18:50,880 --> 00:18:52,882
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau meniruku?</font>

331
00:18:56,252 --> 00:18:57,553
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau takut?</font>

332
00:19:00,789 --> 00:19:02,491
<font color=#FFFF00>Dulu aku...</font>

333
00:19:03,492 --> 00:19:06,962
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku pikir orang tua akan meninggalkanku...</font>

334
00:19:09,131 --> 00:19:11,600
<font color=#FFFF00>...jika aku hidup dalam
bayang-bayang saudaraku.</font>

335
00:19:12,801 --> 00:19:14,069
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku takut.</font>

336
00:19:15,671 --> 00:19:17,339
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu sebabnya aku jadi pemarah.</font>

337
00:19:20,743 --> 00:19:22,244
<font color=#FFFF00>Setiap kali aku marah-marah...,</font>

338
00:19:23,045 --> 00:19:26,182
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau memegang erat tanganku seperti ini.</font>

339
00:19:26,649 --> 00:19:28,117
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau menghiburku.</font>

340
00:19:30,586 --> 00:19:34,823
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau telah melakukan banyak hal
untukku dengan tangan ini.</font>

341
00:19:37,092 --> 00:19:39,595
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau mengajariku cara naik sepeda.</font>

342
00:19:40,529 --> 00:19:42,798
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau memasangkan roda latihan di sepedaku.</font>

343
00:19:44,867 --> 00:19:47,269
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Pak</i>, kau melakukan segalanya...</font>

344
00:19:49,071 --> 00:19:50,906
<font color=#FFFF00>...yang seorang ayah...</font>

345
00:19:53,809 --> 00:19:55,778
<font color=#FFFF00>...biasanya lakukan untuk anaknya.</font>

346
00:20:12,361 --> 00:20:13,929
<font color=#FFFF00>Jae Geol.</font>

347
00:20:14,630 --> 00:20:16,098
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapan kau akan...</font>

348
00:20:16,599 --> 00:20:19,768
<font color=#FFFF00>...berhenti memanggilku Pak?</font>

349
00:20:23,305 --> 00:20:25,140
<font color=#FFFF00>Saat kau kecil...,</font>

350
00:20:25,841 --> 00:20:30,145
<font color=#FFFF00>...Aku membiarkanmu memanggilku Pak
karena kau punya banyak dendam.</font>

351
00:20:30,713 --> 00:20:32,081
<font color=#FFFF00>Namun...,</font>

352
00:20:32,648 --> 00:20:35,251
<font color=#FFFF00>...saat aku sembuh setelah operasi...,</font>

353
00:20:35,451 --> 00:20:36,986
<font color=#FFFF00>...aku akan...</font>

354
00:20:38,287 --> 00:20:42,324
<font color=#FFFF00>...memastikan kalau kau tetap sopan dan santun.</font>

355
00:20:43,025 --> 00:20:44,326
<font color=#FFFF00>Bisakah kita...</font>

356
00:20:46,028 --> 00:20:47,329
<font color=#FFFF00>....melanjutkan operasi?</font>

357
00:21:03,112 --> 00:21:04,847
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau pria.</font>

358
00:21:06,782 --> 00:21:08,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa kau menangis?</font>

359
00:21:15,457 --> 00:21:18,360
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, sudah besar.</font>

360
00:21:21,630 --> 00:21:24,400
<font color=#FFFF00>Kapan tangan Jae Geol...</font>

361
00:21:25,467 --> 00:21:27,636
<font color=#FFFF00>...menjadi sangat besar?</font>

362
00:22:39,108 --> 00:22:40,642
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Lidocaine</i>.</font>

363
00:22:56,392 --> 00:22:57,760
<font color=#FFFF00>Berikan aku satu lagi.</font>

364
00:23:10,152 --> 00:23:12,482
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku merasa sangat cemas.</font>

365
00:23:12,482 --> 00:23:15,722
<font color=#FFFF00>Berhenti bergerak-gerak.
Kau membuatku pusing.</font>

366
00:23:15,722 --> 00:23:18,452
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau tidak punya rasa simpati, ya?</font>

367
00:23:21,261 --> 00:23:23,192
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sedang apa disana?</font>

368
00:23:28,261 --> 00:23:29,561
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau sedang menangis?</font>

369
00:23:29,561 --> 00:23:32,232
<font color=#FFFF00>Apa maksudmu?</font>

370
00:23:32,232 --> 00:23:34,071
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah karena kau khawatir?</font>

371
00:23:34,071 --> 00:23:36,571
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak, bukan begitu.</font>

372
00:23:36,841 --> 00:23:40,511
<font color=#FFFF00>Para dokter dari departemen yang berbeda
bekerja sebagai sebuah tim...</font>

373
00:23:40,511 --> 00:23:43,351
<font color=#FFFF00>...dan berusaha yang terbaik
untuk menyelamatkan pasien.</font>

374
00:23:43,351 --> 00:23:46,551
<font color=#FFFF00>Melihat mereka seperti itu
membuatku emosional.</font>

375
00:23:46,851 --> 00:23:49,682
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja. Aku sangat mengerti.</font>

376
00:23:54,861 --> 00:23:56,091
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Retractor.</i></font>

377
00:24:01,902 --> 00:24:03,002
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Net.</i></font>

378
00:24:03,601 --> 00:24:04,771
<font color=#FFFF00><i>Forceps.</i></font>

379
00:24:11,642 --> 00:24:13,942
<font color=#FFFF00>Tarik <i>retractor</i>-nya sedikit lagi
agar aku bisa melihat lebih jelas.</font>

380
00:24:20,952 --> 00:24:22,252
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak apa-apa.</font>

381
00:24:23,192 --> 00:24:24,992
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu hanya perasaan.</font>

382
00:24:38,732 --> 00:24:41,942
<font color=#FFFF00>Akankah akupunktur benar-benar
membantu mereka membius pasien?</font>

383
00:24:41,942 --> 00:24:44,871
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku tidak yakin. Aku bekerja
di pengobatan Korea...,</font>

384
00:24:44,871 --> 00:24:47,212
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi aku tidak bisa
benar-benar mempercayainya.</font>

385
00:24:49,511 --> 00:24:51,752
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter. Dokter Cha.</font>

386
00:24:51,882 --> 00:24:53,321
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau percaya itu?</font>

387
00:24:53,521 --> 00:24:55,621
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku hanya berdoa...</font>

388
00:24:55,722 --> 00:24:57,452
<font color=#FFFF00>...demi keajaiban.</font>

389
00:25:01,662 --> 00:25:02,761
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter!</font>

390
00:25:04,162 --> 00:25:06,162
<font color=#FFFF00>Kadar oksigen dalam darahnya...</font>

391
00:25:09,031 --> 00:25:12,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa sangat rendah?
Kau yakin pasiennya stabil?</font>

392
00:25:14,271 --> 00:25:15,601
<font color=#FFFF00>Wah, itu mengejutkanku.</font>

393
00:25:15,902 --> 00:25:18,942
<font color=#FFFF00>Maafkan aku. Pasti jatuh
saat kita memindahkan dia.</font>

394
00:25:27,452 --> 00:25:28,752
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo lanjutkan.</font>

395
00:25:29,992 --> 00:25:32,291
<font color=#FFFF00>Berapa banyak waktu yang kita miliki?</font>

396
00:25:32,291 --> 00:25:34,162
<font color=#FFFF00>13 menit.</font>

397
00:25:44,132 --> 00:25:45,571
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini membuatku gila.</font>

398
00:25:47,601 --> 00:25:48,841
<font color=#FFFF00>Dokter.</font>

399
00:25:49,371 --> 00:25:51,472
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana... Bagaimana hasilnya?</font>

400
00:25:53,011 --> 00:25:55,311
<font color=#FFFF00>Operasinya berjalan lancar, kan?</font>

401
00:25:55,841 --> 00:25:58,752
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja.
/ Iya! Itu berhasil.</font>

402
00:25:59,182 --> 00:26:02,051
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana?
/ Apa maksudmu, bagaimana?</font>

403
00:26:02,382 --> 00:26:04,521
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah akupunktur benar-benar membius dia?</font>

404
00:26:04,521 --> 00:26:06,821
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayolah, itu tidak mungkin.</font>

405
00:26:06,821 --> 00:26:09,321
<font color=#FFFF00>Aku ingin mendapatkan akupunktur sendiri...,</font>

406
00:26:09,462 --> 00:26:11,061
<font color=#FFFF00>...tapi itu tidak mungkin.</font>

407
00:26:11,432 --> 00:26:13,632
<font color=#FFFF00>Pak Park sudah melakukan pekerjaan yang hebat
dengan menahan itu, bukannya kau, Jae Geol.</font>

408
00:26:13,632 --> 00:26:15,902
<font color=#FFFF00>Mungkin dia putus asa menahan rasa sakit
untuk membuatmu terlihat baik.</font>

409
00:26:15,902 --> 00:26:17,202
<font color=#FFFF00>Tidak mungkin.</font>

410
00:26:17,432 --> 00:26:20,041
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana bisa seseorang menahan
rasa sakit saat operasi pembedahan?</font>

411
00:26:20,871 --> 00:26:23,611
<font color=#FFFF00>Bukankah begitu, Dokter Song?</font>

412
00:26:25,912 --> 00:26:27,111
<font color=#FFFF00>Tentu saja.</font>

413
00:26:27,712 --> 00:26:31,081
<font color=#FFFF00>Itu bukan rasa sakit yang bisa
kau tahan dengan kemauan.</font>

414
00:26:33,682 --> 00:26:37,021
<font color=#FFFF00>Apakah dia berpihak pada
seorang dokter medis Korea juga?</font>

415
00:26:37,021 --> 00:26:39,992
<font color=#FFFF00>Kau dengar itu?
Seharusnya kau diam paling tidak.</font>

416
00:26:40,021 --> 00:26:42,692
<font color=#FFFF00>Jae Geol, ayolah. Jangan marah.</font>

417
00:26:42,692 --> 00:26:43,892
<font color=#FFFF00>Jangan mengikutiku.</font>

418
00:27:25,232 --> 00:27:26,402
<font color=#FFFF00>Ini.</font>

419
00:27:27,502 --> 00:27:28,902
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo, ambilah.</font>

420
00:27:32,942 --> 00:27:34,382
<font color=#FFFF00>Akan kupastikan...</font>

421
00:27:35,242 --> 00:27:37,511
<font color=#FFFF00>...untuk membalasmu kembali
suatu hari nanti.</font>

422
00:27:40,152 --> 00:27:42,781
<font color=#FFFF00>Kerja bagus. Bersulang.</font>

423
00:27:55,301 --> 00:27:58,232
<font color=#FFFF00>Sekarang, giliranmu.</font>

424
00:28:02,041 --> 00:28:04,212
<font color=#FFFF00><i>"Kerja bagus, Dokter Kim."</i></font>

425
00:28:04,611 --> 00:28:07,581
<font color=#FFFF00><i>"Aku bisa menyelamatkan pasien,
terima kasih untukmu."</i></font>

426
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:11,900
<font color=#FFFF00><i>(Episode 18 akan segera tayang.)</i></font>

